01:05.120 --> 01:06.109
Yeah.

01:06.280 --> 01:08.020
Yeah. Sorry about the mess.

01:08.120 --> 01:10.827
You boys just took down an evil plushie
that was trying to kill me.

01:10.920 --> 01:11.909
