01:19.920 --> 01:23.026
What in the... What? Holy heck...

01:23.680 --> 01:24.669
It was...

01:24.760 --> 01:25.749
Did they do this?

01:25.840 --> 01:26.829
No. Naw, it was...

01:27.240 --> 01:29.219
Defective product. Yeah.

01:29.440 --> 01:34.343
_Sometimes the batteries in these
giant stuffed dinosaurs Just explode.

01:34.480 --> 01:36.300
Yeah, never buy anything
from Mooselyvania.

01:36.400 --> 01:37.389
Exactly.

01:38.640 --> 01:39.629
Okay.

01:40.320 --> 01:43.266
Guys, this is Jay, he's the big man
around this neighborhood.

01:43.360 --> 01:47.820
Owns practically the whole damn thing.
The Chinese joint, the laundromat...

01:47.960 --> 01:52.306
Great. Great, great. That's very cool.
Can you guys give us a second? Great.

01:52.400 --> 01:53.389
Nice cover.

01:53.480 --> 01:54.469
What the hell was that?

01:54.560 --> 01:57.142
I mean, we rolled into town because
people were seeing a lizard monster.

01:57.240 --> 01:59.504
And, yes, we tracked it back here,
but no way did I think we'd end up--

01:59.640 --> 02:01.187
- Killing Barney?
- Yeah.

02:01.360 --> 02:05.103
Was pretty satisfying though, wasn't it?
It was probably just a cursed object.

02:05.200 --> 02:06.303
Well, it didn't act like
a cursed object.

02:06.680 --> 02:07.669
We should probably do some digging.

02:08.480 --> 02:09.469
Everything all right?

02:13.040 --> 02:14.302
Yeah, yeah. Great.

02:14.400 --> 02:15.981
Yeah. No, we were just gonna head out.

02:16.160 --> 02:22.986
Oh! Hold up. You boys saved my life.
Anything you want? It's yours.

02:23.320 --> 02:25.697
