- Shh!

03:03.720 --> 03:04.823
Hey, what are you doing?

03:06.400 --> 03:07.389
Research.

03:07.720 --> 03:08.709
Okay.

03:08.800 --> 03:13.180
You know, it's the strangest thing,
I can't find anything on a cursed object

03:13.280 --> 03:15.544
