03:15.640 --> 03:19.747
Dude, it's over, all right.
Be like Elsa, "Let it go."

03:24.080 --> 03:25.069
"Be like Elsa"?

03:25.280 --> 03:26.599
Aha! Right?

03:27.680 --> 03:30.660
Come here, I need to show you something.
It's important. Come on.

03:35.440 --> 03:41.345
Behold. The Dean-cave.
Or Fortress of Dean-atude.

03:41.440 --> 03:43.783
Just-- Still trying to figure
that one out.

03:43.880 --> 03:47.759
We got foosball. We got jukebox,
all vinyl, obviously.

03:48.400 --> 03:52.905
Double Lay-Z-Boy recliners.
And of course, the bar.

03:53.000 --> 03:53.989
Still a work in progress.

03:54.080 --> 03:55.342
It's gonna have a Kegerator, because...

03:55.920 --> 03:57.023
Well, it's gonna.

03:57.280 --> 04:01.262
And finally, the pice de rsistance.

04:01.360 --> 04:02.429
Okay, hold on. Hold on.

04:03.080 --> 04:04.399
