04:05.040 --> 04:06.667
When it's important,
you make time, Sammy.

04:07.840 --> 04:09.944
Let's give this bad boy a test run, huh?

04:10.640 --> 04:14.827
Da-da-dah.

04:15.320 --> 04:20.587
(DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING)

04:24.080 --> 04:25.069
