04:37.400 --> 04:40.039
You're a cartoon! I'm a cartoon!

04:40.640 --> 04:43.382
Is this a...
Okay, okay, okay, this is a dream.

04:43.480 --> 04:45.186
It's gotta be a... Dude?

04:46.640 --> 04:48.779
It's not a dream. Holy crap.

04:49.440 --> 04:51.226
This... This, uh...

04:51.320 --> 04:54.869
You saw that light.
Did we just get sucked into the TV?

04:54.960 --> 04:58.782
Or maybe this is an angel thing?
Or the Trickster?

04:58.880 --> 05:01.098
- No, he's dead.
- Or is he?

05:01.800 --> 05:03.825
Dean, what the hell?

05:04.000 --> 05:06.184
I don't know, Sam. I... Woah!

05:08.440 --> 05:10.385
How did the car get here?

05:10.480 --> 05:12.789
I had the keys in my pocket,
or maybe... Wait--

05:12.880 --> 05:14.825
