about this?

05:14.960 --> 05:19.704
Okay, look, are we animated? Yes.
Is it weird? Yes.

05:19.880 --> 05:21.586
It's beyond weird.

05:21.680 --> 05:23.784
Well, and "beyond weird"
is kind of our thing.

05:23.960 --> 05:26.224
So, whatever happened,
we'll figure it out.

05:26.440 --> 05:29.022
