Look, let's just head in, ask around,
see what we can see.

05:49.480 --> 05:50.583
Oh, my God.

05:51.040 --> 05:52.940
That's".That's".

05:53.160 --> 05:54.229
DEAN: That's the Mystery Machine.

05:55.400 --> 05:58.380
- We're not in just any cartoon...
- We're in Scooby-Doo.

06:14.240 --> 06:16.879
