in a pool of their own blood.

16:10.120 --> 16:11.906
Yeah, yeah, okay, um...

16:12.000 --> 16:15.822
So, if that guy can die for real
in this cartoon,

16:16.120 --> 16:17.439
that means we can, too.

16:17.680 --> 16:20.342
It doesn't matter if we die.
Scooby-doo could die!

16:20.440 --> 16:22.260
