to collect an inheritance?

16:31.960 --> 16:33.302
Yeah. What he said.

16:33.480 --> 16:35.266
What would a ghost need with money?

16:35.360 --> 16:36.384
Precisely.

16:36.480 --> 16:38.903
And besides,
there's no such thing as ghosts.

16:39.080 --> 16:41.264
So, once you eliminate the impossible,

16:41.360 --> 16:43.920
whatever remains,
no matter how improbable,

16:44.000 --> 16:45.137
must be the truth.

